	<li><a href="https://celebrat.net/category/news/" rel="category tag">News</a></li></ul>				</div>
						<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://celebrat.net/eus-digital-omnibus-marks-a-regulatory-pivot-on-ai-and-everyones-reading-the-fine-print/" rel="bookmark">EU’s “Digital Omnibus” Marks a Regulatory Pivot on AI and Everyone’s Reading the Fine Print</a></h2>				<ul class="entry-meta">
											<li class="post-author"> <a href="https://celebrat.net/author/admin/"><span class="far fa-user"></span>admin</a></li>
																<li class="post-date"> <span class="far fa-calendar-alt"></span>January 19, 2026</li>
										<li class="post-comment"> <span class="far fa-comment"></span>0</li>
				</ul>
						<div class="post-content">
				<p>The European Commission has just unveiled its “Digital Omnibus” proposal, a bold step in its ongoing effort to regulate artificial intelligence (AI) across the continent. [&hellip;]</p>
